---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms · thelnk.is" description="Terms of use for thelnk.is.">
  <article class="legal">
    <h1>Terms of use</h1>
    <p class="lead">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <p>
      These terms govern your use of thelnk.is. By creating an account or using the service, you agree to
      them. If you don't agree, please don't use the service.
    </p>

    <h2>The service</h2>
    <p>
      thelnk.is lets you claim a username and publish a public link-in-bio page. The service is provided
      “as-is.” We may add, change, limit, or discontinue features, and we'll make reasonable efforts to
      give notice of material changes where practicable.
    </p>

    <h2>Your account</h2>
    <p>
      You're responsible for activity under your account and for keeping your sign-in secure. You must
      provide accurate information and be at least 13 years old to use the service.
    </p>

    <h2>Usernames</h2>
    <p>
      Usernames are assigned on a first-come basis and remain yours while your account is active and in
      good standing. We may reclaim or reassign a username that impersonates someone, infringes a
      trademark, is used in bad faith (including squatting), or violates these terms. Don't register
      usernames you don't intend to use.
    </p>

    <h2>Your content</h2>
    <p>
      You own the content you add to your page. You grant thelnk.is the limited license needed to host,
      store, and display that content for the purpose of operating the service. You're responsible for
      your content and confirm you have the rights to publish it and the links you add.
    </p>

    <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
    <p>
      Don't use thelnk.is to distribute malware, run phishing or scams, harass or endanger others, publish
      illegal content, infringe intellectual property, or spam. We may suspend or remove pages, links, or
      accounts that abuse the service, harm others, or threaten its stability.
    </p>

    <h2>Selling and payments</h2>
    <p>
      Commerce features (products, tickets, tips) are not yet available. When they launch, additional
      terms and a third-party payment processor will apply, and you'll be responsible for the legality and
      fulfillment of anything you sell.
    </p>

    <h2>Termination</h2>
    <p>
      You can stop using the service and request deletion of your account at any time. We may suspend or
      terminate accounts that violate these terms. On termination, your public page and stored profile
      data may be removed.
    </p>

    <h2>Disclaimer & liability</h2>
    <p>
      To the maximum extent permitted by law, the service is provided without warranties of any kind, and
      we are not liable for indirect or consequential damages arising from its use.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update these terms as the product evolves. Continued use after changes take effect means you
      accept the updated terms.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:hello@thelnk.is">hello@thelnk.is</a>.</p>

    <p class="back"><a href="/">← Back home</a></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem) 1.5rem 4rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .legal h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }
  .legal .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--muted-2);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }
  .legal h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 2.25rem 0 0.6rem;
  }
  .legal p { margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  .legal a { color: var(--accent); }
  .legal a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .legal strong { color: var(--text-dim); }
  .legal .back { margin-top: 2.5rem; }
</style>
